<i>adverb</i>: 듬직이 [듬지기], 든든히 [든든히], 두터이 [두터이], 돈독히 [돈도키] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>듬직이 [듬지기]</dt><br>
<dd>1. reliably</dd><br>
<dd>모습이나 성격이 점잖고 믿음직하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner that one's behavior or personality looks dependable and decent.</dd><br>
<dd>2. gravely; imposingly</dd><br>
<dd>사물의 겉모양이 크고 당당하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which the outward look of an object is big and imposing.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>든든히 [든든히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. reassuringly</dd><br>
<dd>무엇에 대한 믿음으로 의지가 되고 마음이 놓이게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that makes someone feel secure and rely on someone on the basis of trust in him/her.</dd><br>
<dd>2. strongly; robustly</dd><br>
<dd>물건이나 몸이 알차고 야무지게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which an object or body is solid and sturdy.</dd><br>
<dd>3. reliably</dd><br>
<dd>믿을 만할 정도로 알차고 실하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being so solid and substantial as to be reliable.</dd><br>
<dd>4. strongly; firmly</dd><br>
<dd>품은 생각이나 뜻이 강하고 야무지게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which one's ambition or wish is firm and strong.</dd><br>
<dd>5. fully</dd><br>
<dd>먹은 것이나 입은 것이 충분하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of eating or wearing enough.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>두터이 [두터이]</dt><br>
<dd>closely; reliably</dd><br>
<dd>믿음, 관계, 인정 등이 굳고 깊게.</dd><br>
<dd>Trust, relationship, etc., being strong and deep.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>돈독히 [돈도키]</dt><br>
<dd>closely; reliably</dd><br>
<dd>믿음, 의리, 인정 등이 깊고 성실하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Trustworthily, faithfully, compassionately, and sincerely.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>